 inspection body must comply with a number of obligations to retain its accreditation.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.dev-vlaanderen.be/informatie-voor-de-keuringsinstelling-voor-de-keuring-van-koeltechnische-bedrijven\">More info on the obligations for accredited inspection bodies.</a></p><p> </p>",
